Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This blade has a dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It has shed much innocent blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fool for traveling alone,\Nso completely unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky your blood's still flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you to\Nthe land of the gatekeepers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone very dear?\NA kindred spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous quest for a lone hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been alone for\Nas long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost done. Shhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, Scales! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Scales?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only failed to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These are dragon lands, Sintel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are closer than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Scales?
